Honeywell,is,a,security,company,that,provides,security,services,and,devices,for,homes,and,businesses,AlarmNet,Direct,is,a,web,based,service,designed,to,let,users,communicate,with,Honeywell,s,security,devices,remotely,It,allows,customers,to,register,program,command,and,check,the,status,of,devices,over,the,internet,These,functions,can,also,be,accessed,programmatically,using,the,AlarmNet,Direct,SOAP,API